        " : \"لاَ تُقْبَلُ شَهَادَةُ ذِي شَحْنَاءَ أَوْ ذِي مُخْزِيَةٍ فِي اَلدِّينِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3288 - And Isma'il bin Muslim narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), from his forefathers, peace be upon them, who said:\n\"The testimony of one who harbors enmity or one who has a disgraceful reputation in religion is not accepted.\""
        ]
      }
